item.title: Teleblock-is in the emote tab-help please-
item.dc:creator: @ChemicalReaction1 ChemicalReaction™
item.description:
@ChemicalReaction1 wrote:

right click on the bit that says home
and search that number in client.java
search

case ###

( ### reprresents the numbers )

when you found. Make it look like this :

case ###: if(!teleblock) { teleportToX = Xcoord; teleportToY = Ycoord; } else if(teleblock) { sendMessage("A magical force stops you from teleporting."); } } break;
